Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:43.23,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:48.24,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell us where Turtle--\NI mean Noboru Maeda-- is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:55.48,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I can't.\NI don't know who you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:57.56,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--Listen, old man!\N--Mario!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:02.77,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:06.84,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, won't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:11.58,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to take him to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:16.65,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like this is important...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:26.50,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,He's over in Mishuku,\Ncollecting some money I lent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:27.93,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Collecting money?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:31.66,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,With any luck, he'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:35.66,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dealing with a\Nrather vicious sort, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:41.39,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I've agreed to lend him money if he\Ncan successfully collect the loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:43.64,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Money? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.90,0:03:48.13,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,For his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:53.12,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:04:00.78,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,How much would it cost to make\Nyour little dream come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.99,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be, that Noboru...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:13.09,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm going to Mishuku!\N--Wait! I'm coming too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:16.23,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Lilly! You heard him!\NWe're dealing with--!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:19.54,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! He's doing this for me--!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:30.01,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:33.99,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Walk faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:35.25,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:37.97,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:44.52,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario... Lilly...\NWhat are you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.81,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? You suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:51.05,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's the matter, Lilly?\NWhy the gloomy--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:55.91,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:04.01,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Lilly? Hey...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:05.95,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:09.94,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot..!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:17.08,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, now! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:31.32,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She had cried out of \Nsadness and frustration before,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.83,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but never out of happiness, until now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:36.39,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lilly had always struggled\Nto survive on her own{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:43.67,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in this world devoid of\Nkindness and compassion...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:50.58,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Turtle considered her family now...\NHe risked his life for her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:55.74,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lilly couldn't stop her tears.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:04.61,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... It was very nice\Nof you to see me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:08.19,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right. Nice, my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:12.22,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:15.79,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid almost bit it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:26.76,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay! I'll go! I'll go\Npay the interest! Just let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:35.16,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not funny! That's one hell\Nof an animal you picked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:38.46,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no wonder them call him "Turtle"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:46.86,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,"The next day"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:47.05,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0410,,--Let's go!\N--No! I refuse to get a check-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:50.93,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--Knock it off, Turtle!\N--Shut up! Let go, Mario!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:55.09,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor already said it was a cold!\NI'm perfectly fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.08,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Noboru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:06:59.75,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to get tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:03.22,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in the atomic blast, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:09.12,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario! You told her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:15.39,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Turtle. You told Mr. Sugi\Nyou need money for your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:18.41,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You were talking\Nabout Lilly, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:26.05,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you know what she was doing\Nwhile you were risking your life for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:27.97,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:32.70,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,She had to put up\Nwith some terrible things
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.68,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,to get the hospital here\Nto take a look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:39.16,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you were the one who did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:41.35,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:46.95,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Turtle.\NLilly's in the same boat as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:50.68,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't stop worrying about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:53.62,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,She thinks of you as a little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:59.28,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're family, then you\Nhave to listen to your big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:04.67,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:06.99,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Lilly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:12.60,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! I don't remember ever having\Nsuch an unreasonable little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:18.99,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:30.45,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeffrey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:33.93,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to see us? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:40.31,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Noboru Maeda, yes? I'll be your \Ninterpreter today, so you can rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:41.77,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:47.48,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Mario. I'm heading out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:49.91,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:53.23,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Just some minor business.\NI leave the rest here to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:56.37,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Lilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:10.35,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:14.86,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario. You really gave up boxing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:19.02,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I know a good trainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:24.50,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,If he can take a look at you, your fist might still be of some use.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:29.44,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it? You wanna go for another shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:33.95,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Jeffrey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:38.30,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand a thing you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:39.45,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:45.04,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.02,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:51.00,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,They said to come back in a week,\Nwhen they'll have the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:52.63,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:55.48,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's go.\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:58.92,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, Jeffrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.91,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I had fun boxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:10.12,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where's Lilly?\N--Said she had stuff to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:10.92,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:18.31,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.52,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:38.35,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,If not, I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:43.82,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That child...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:50.45,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't lend him--\NNoboru-- any money...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:11:02.84,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't lend him--\NNoboru-- any money...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:05.80,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:08.92,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to disappear from his sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:14.18,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,So please don't give him\Nany more dangerous work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:17.96,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:21.10,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to burden him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:23.56,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:29.23,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really how a family works?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.90,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I will lend him the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:41.23,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave him my conditions, and he fulfilled them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:45.22,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,This agreement is between the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:47.13,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's for..!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:48.91,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your concern,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:54.88,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,even more so if you're about\Nto disappear from his sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:11:59.34,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:04.78,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:09.29,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:14.80,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be willing to buy me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.85,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:32.76,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,"One week later"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:35.07,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0410,,"The results of last week's tests\Nshow nothing out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:39.44,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing requiring treatment was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:45.37,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we can't rule out the possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:47.42,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,of future after-effects of the atomic blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:52.69,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Recommend regular tests from now on."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:59.29,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, Turtle! What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:06.66,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the stern face? You should be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:10.52,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you act so carefree?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:11.29,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:13.67,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about Lilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:19.49,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been gone for a week now...\NWhere could she be!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:26.49,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:30.13,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh? Where to?\N--To see Mr. Sugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:33.54,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised to tell him about\Nyour test results, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:36.23,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:42.60,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! I'm glad to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:45.70,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:49.06,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:52.19,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't need it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:55.50,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Is our tea ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:57.17,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.04,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lilly!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:17.61,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the good news about\Nyour test results! That's a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:20.51,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You've really taken to your new job, Lilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:21.73,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:24.56,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:30.36,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here, Mr. Sugi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:31.60,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Turtle...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:38.13,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You old pervert!\NYou bought Lilly, didn't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.15,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Noboru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:45.38,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to you for help so she\Nwouldn't have to do this sort of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:49.46,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You acted friendly-like and\Ntricked her into doing this..!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:52.08,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too old to buy women anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.83,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--Calm down, Turtle!\N--Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:56.61,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario! You were in on this too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:10.98,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:18.14,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What are you laughing at!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:21.56,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Turtle! Don't get mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:25.70,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Your reaction was just so\Nclose to what I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.91,0:15:29.93,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Noboru.\NI'll explain everything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:35.36,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to see Mr. Sugi\Nthe day of your check-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.24,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be willing to buy me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:46.25,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,If you buy me, Noboru won't\Nhave to go through with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:48.08,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:53.89,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You truly don't understand how he feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:16:00.95,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,He risked his life so you\Nwouldn't have to resort to such work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.55,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:13.61,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I told Mr. Sugi everything after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:18.89,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,About how I had made a living before...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:24.56,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,About how I milked money from\Nthat army officer to start my own shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:27.92,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,And how he ran off with it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:33.86,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,As I talked, I started to realize\Nhow much I despised myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:40.19,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You should thank that military officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:41.29,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:45.58,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you had started\Na business with that money,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:48.23,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,you would have been\Ndrowning in debt before long
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.80,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,and stripped of everything you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:52.77,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:58.40,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,A business is not something\Nto be approached lightly, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:00.91,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what do you suggest I do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:04.90,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What else is there for me to do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:14.29,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Having a house this\Nlarge makes it difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:16.55,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,for an old man to\Nproperly clean on his own...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:20.19,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I can offer you 15,000 yen a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:21.32,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:25.15,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You can work as a live-in maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:30.00,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Spend a year or two here\Nto learn and understand
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:36.66,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,what it means to work and\Nwhat it means to run a business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:41.63,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Noboru Maeda is still young,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:45.07,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,but he has a good grasp\Non what a business entails.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.98,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time you\Nmaster running a business,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:51.39,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,the 300,000 yen I lent\Nwill have grown significantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:55.31,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,probably even enough\Nto open your own shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:03.29,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're a live-in maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:04.70,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:13.73,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sugi! I'm sorry about\Nthe terrible things I just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:17.05,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take good care of Lilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:19.00,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Noboru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:22.29,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll borrow this money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:26.95,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, I start\Nworking hard as a 1% lender!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:37.09,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,One more drink..!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:40.01,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you drink too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:45.73,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess it's a real relief after\Nyour tests came back negative
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.15,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,and finding out Lilly's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:55.39,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Mr. Sugi live alone\Nin such a big house anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:06.36,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it you're wondering why\NI live alone in such a large house?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:07.60,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.28,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:24.61,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these..?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:32.52,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,My wife has already passed on,\Nbut I built this house for our sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:37.83,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been sent their remains,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:44.34,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,and their war buddies\Ndidn't see them die, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:47.24,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,So they will be back someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:52.15,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I have faith that they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:19:58.42,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Booze..!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:02.22,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're a lost cause.\NKnock it off, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:04.67,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:10.05,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Noboru really is in good health, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:11.91,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:19.92,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it ever takes a turn for the worse,\Nwe'll make sure he survives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:22.91,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna earn a ton!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:24.71,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:31.34,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll carry him now, Mario.\N--Huh? No, that's okay. He's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:33.02,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:39.28,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:57.35,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A heavy load for one person\Nbecomes lighter when carried by several.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:02.95,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lilly, having experienced family ties\Nfor the first time in her life,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:09.80,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}decided to live from now\Non for herself and for Turtle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:16.03,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Noboru...
